{"article_id":"SHaeJVogd3LYNdDN","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"When it comes to the nomination of Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh ,","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"remember one thing :","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Either the math works in favor of Kavanaugh","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"or it doesn ' t .","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"The Senate is divided between 51 Republicans and 49 senators","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"who caucus with Democrats .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Forty-five Republicans have said","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"they will support Kavanaugh .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Six GOPers remain undecided .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"They are Sens . Susan Collins , R-Maine ; Bob Corker , R-Tenn. ; Mike Enzi , R-Wyo . ; Jeff Flake , R-Ariz. ; Jerry Moran , R-Kan. ; and Lisa Murkowski , R-Alaska .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"In the very near future , Judge Kavanaugh will be on the United States Supreme Court .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"- Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"There are at least four Republican senators","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"who are genuinely in play right now .","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"Fox News is told","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"the number could be as high as seven Republicans .","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"The four obvious ones on the fence are Collins , Corker , Flake and Murkowski .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"\" In the very near future , Judge Kavanaugh will be on the United States Supreme Court , \"","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"said McConnell in a speech at the Values Voters Summit on Friday .","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"\" So my friends , keep the faith . \"","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"\" Judge Kavanaugh will be voted on here on the Senate floor .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"Up or down , on the Senate floor , this fine nominee to the Supreme Court will receive a vote in this Senate in the near future , \"","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"said McConnell .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"\" We ' re in the Twilight Zone","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"when it comes to Kavanaugh , \"","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"said Sen. Lindsey Graham , R-S.C .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"That ' s why the nomination is struggling .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Kavanaugh refuses to withdraw .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"He appeared on Fox News on Monday night","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"to dispute the allegations","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"leveled against him","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"by Christine Blasey Ford and others .","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"Know this :","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"a nominee on the verge","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"of sailing to confirmation","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"doesn ' t appear on national television with his wife","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"to make his case .","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"So , Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell , R-Ky. , is trying to salvage the nomination .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"McConnell delivered a blistering speech on the Senate floor Monday afternoon .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"He upbraided Democrats over the methods","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"to sink Kavanaugh","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"and simultaneously rallied Republicans to the fore .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"In addition , this may have been a signal by McConnell to President Trump","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"that he ' s going to the mat for the nominee .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"After all , the Senate is in play this fall .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"The open seat on the High Court is a swing vote .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"If Kavanaugh stumbles ,","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"Republicans may struggle to fill the vacancy with a conservative voice .","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"Baseball clubs","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"eliminated from the pennant race","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"often mail it in over last few weeks of the season .","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"Some Kavanaugh advocates fear","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"that could be the case here .","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"McConnell knows","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"GOPers won ' t have any chance","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"if they don ' t run through the base on every ground ball in an effort","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"to rescue the nomination .","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"Moreover , forging ahead with a vote could help Republicans in the midterms .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Holding a vote could be a tactic","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"to force moderate Democratic senators","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"facing competitive re-election bids from red states ,","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"to declare their position on Kavanaugh .","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"No free passes .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"This approach was part of the GOP game plan with Kavanaugh from the start .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"So why not stick to the playbook ?","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Republicans might not install Kavanaugh on the High Court .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"But they can at least weaponize a roll call vote against Sens .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"Joe Manchin , D-WVa . ; Heidi Heitkamp , D-N.D. ; Joe Donnelly , D-Ind . ; Jon Tester , D-Mont . ; Claire McCaskill , D-Mo. , and a host of others in an effort","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"to bolster Senate Republicans .","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"Fox News spoke with multiple Republican senators Monday .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"All say","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"they want to hear from Ford .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"But many senators confided","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"they could in fact vote against Kavanaugh","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"if they hear something alarming in Thursday ' s testimony .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"By the same token , many Republican senators are worried about establishing a precedent","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"which could upend someone ' s career","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"based on impossible-to-prove allegations .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"Also , there is a chance","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"that Democrats may overplay their hand on Kavanaugh .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"There is chatter on Capitol Hill","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"that efforts","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"to undermine Kavanaugh ' s nomination","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"could boomerang against the Democrats just before the election .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"Considering the controversy","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"involving Kavanaugh ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"most senators on Capitol Hill Monday would have preferred to have discussed the fate of Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"[ W ]","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"hile I am frightened ,","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"please know ,","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"my fear will not hold me back from testifying .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"- Christine Blasey Ford","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"It was possible until Monday afternoon that McConnell could yank Kavanaugh ' s nomination off the floor","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"if he lacked the votes for confirmation .","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"In mid-July , the Senate was moments away from taking a voting on the nomination of Ryan Bounds for a seat on the 9th Circuit Court of Appeals .","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"But senators unearthed some racist writings by Bounds","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"and discovered","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"he held some controversial views .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"Sen. Tim Scott , R-S.C. , is the only African American GOPer in the Senate .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"Scott met with Bounds","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"and reported to McConnell","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"that he couldn ' t support the nomination .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"Bounds lacked the votes for confirmation .","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"McConnell abruptly cancelled the confirmation vote","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"and President Trump withdrew the nomination .","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"So all eyes will focus on the Thursday hearing","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"with Ford appearing first ,","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"followed by Kavanaugh .","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"In a letter to Grassley , Ford declared","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"\" while I am frightened ,","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"please know ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"my fear will not hold me back from testifying. \"","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"In a return missive to Ford , Grassley wrote in the margin","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"\" P.S . :","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"I look forward to your testimony . \"","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"Thursday ' s forum won ' t play out in the commodious , TV-friendly hearing facility in the Hart Senate Office Building ,","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"constructed for major events such as this one .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"Instead , the Judiciary Committee will convene in a much smaller room in the Dirksen Senate Office Building .","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"Keep in mind","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"that in her letter to Grassley , Ford said","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"she wants a hearing","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"that won ' t \" become a media TV show . \"","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"As for a committee vote , it ' s not out of the question for the panel to announce","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"there could be a committee vote on Kavanaugh later that day .","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"even if Grassley \" notices \" a committee vote for Thursday ,","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"he can delay the vote .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"Senators from both sides of the aisle need time","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"to process what Kavanaugh and Ford said .","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"That ' s why a floor vote on Kavanaugh won ' t unfold until next Tuesday at the earliest .","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"And win or lose ,","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"the math is the math is the math .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":263,"left":135,"right":262,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":135,"left":133,"right":134,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":133,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":134,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":262,"left":222,"right":261,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":222,"left":197,"right":221,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":140,"right":196,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":136,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":137,"right":138,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":137,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":138,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":156,"right":195,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":152,"right":155,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":141,"right":151,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":145,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":144,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":142,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":147,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":146,"right":19,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":146,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"